{"tid":975853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真●環保]就應該減少人口同車","createTime":"2019-01-10T03:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T03:51:37.000Z","uid":122823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a998299d52772ab1ad78907020cc65acf9fb2ab4","tid":975853,"uid":122823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/135845_1e6814108a523197bd105e9c08e3f7b7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F135845_1e6814108a523197bd105e9c08e3f7b7.gif&h=25e332fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/143627/thumbnail/8a36a49d56ef7194e1220f03fec0076c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F143627%2Fthumbnail%2F8a36a49d56ef7194e1220f03fec0076c.jpg&h=c9be4542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日日放幾百個落嚟,人多就自然多垃圾啦,車多就用多咗油又多癈氣,環境嚴重空氣污染,<br />\n人口太多醫療嚴重不足,香港人冇公屋住,樓又冇錢買<br />\n<img src=\"http://spider.nosdn.127.net/3562271953cc435a78aaa30033dad2ac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspider.nosdn.127.net%2F3562271953cc435a78aaa30033dad2ac.gif&h=444d010f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應該鼓勵香港人多啲踩單車代步,更改過時嘅法例,運動多咗身體自然好,重邊洗成日去睇醫生呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://ny-gps.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/shutterstock_1012257106-e1527284673996-1280x640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fny-gps.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Fshutterstock_1012257106-e1527284673996-1280x640.jpg&h=68ad3aa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/10/03/10100347_577606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F10%2F03%2F10100347_577606.jpg&h=831e0b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自備水壺/杯,減少買即棄飲品,快餐店應該換可循環嘅餐具,而唔係一味走飲筒<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做個高質連登仔一定要貼圖呢</span></span></strong>"}]}